                    "line_text": "je ne bois que de l'eau glacée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Et de sa seule panacée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Mes tissus qui stagnent ont faim.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mets de la lune dans ton vin,\nM'a dit sa moue cadenassée ;\nje ne bois que de l'eau glacée,\nEt de sa seule panacée\nMes tissus qui stagnent ont faim."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Lune, consomme mon baptême,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Lave mes yeux de ton linceul ;",
